snippet.title: UCL
snippet.description:
UCL (University College London) is consistently ranked among the world's top ten universities (QS World University Rankings 2010 - 2025). Our excellence extends across all academic disciplines, from one of the world's foremost centres for research and teaching in the biological sciences to world-renowned centres for architecture (The Bartlett), education (IOE, Faculty of Education and Society) and fine art (Slade School of Fine Art). 

UCL is London's leading multidisciplinary university, with more than 16,000 staff and 51,000 students from 150 different countries. Founded in 1826 in the heart of London, UCL was the first university in England to welcome students of any religion and the first to welcome women on equal terms with men. 

UCL Minds brings together UCL’s knowledge, insights, and ideas through events, activities, and digital content open to everyone. Find out what’s on UCL Minds: www.ucl.ac.uk/minds

snippet.title: TRT World
snippet.description:
At TRT World we're building a global community focused around change. We’re looking beyond the headlines to drive meaningful conversations that empower. We want to connect people across the globe to issues that matter. We explore the reality behind the hashtags and the people behind the statistics. We will seek to unpack the issues behind each story.

By placing the human at the heart of each story we hope to promote a global conscience that provokes moral reactions - revealing a deeper understanding of the diversity of the lives around us.

Subscribe to our channel for all our latest in-depth, on the ground reporting from around the world.

snippet.title: Kiel Institute for the World Economy
snippet.description:
The Kiel Institute is an international center for research in global economic affairs, economic policy consulting, and economic education. The Institute engages especially in creating solutions to urgent problems in global economic affairs. On basis of its research, the Institute advises decision-takers in policy, business, and society and informs the broader public about important developments in international economic policy.
-- 
Das Institut für Weltwirtschaft an der Universität Kiel (IfW) ist eines der großen Zentren weltwirtschaftlicher Forschung, wirtschaftspolitischer Beratung und ökonomischer Ausbildung. Das Institut sieht seine Hauptaufgabe in der Erforschung innovativer Lösungsansätze für drängende weltwirtschaftliche Probleme. Auf Basis dieser Forschungsarbeiten berät es Entscheidungsträger in Politik, Wirtschaft und Gesellschaft und informiert die interessierte Öffentlichkeit über wichtige wirtschaftspolitische Zusammenhänge.

snippet.title: UKspreadbetting
snippet.description:
🔴 Trading is Risky! 70% to 89% of retail investors lose money!  Financial-Spread-Betting.com is where betting and finance meets, on the trading floor.  This is a place where we can inform, and educate little, and hopefully entertain a little too.

Spread betting is an efficient way to trade the financial markets as you pay no stamp duty or CGT on any profits you make. This is because the activity is regulated as gambling, as opposed to investing, which means spread traders don't normally pay taxes on their winnings.  The flipside of this is that with spread betting you cannot offset losses against your profits for capital gains tax purposes.

Leverage can amplify both your gains and losses since they are calculated based on the total exposure of the trade, not merely the margin needed to initiate it. Consequently, losses and profits could far outweigh your margin, so always ensure you’re trading within your means.

snippet.title: Fomo Finance
snippet.description:
Herzlich Wilkommen!
Auf unserem Youtube-Kanal, sowie unserer Website und Facebook-Site, veröffentlichen wir regelmäßig Videos und Artikel rund um die Themen Traden und Investieren.
Wir haben uns dabei auf folgende Gebiete spezialisiert:

- Optionen/Optionshandel
- Futures-Handel
- Technische Analyse
- Intermarketanalyse
- Commitments Of Traders
- passives Investieren mit ETFs

Einerseits findes Du Lerninhalte zu den genannten Themen; andererseits besprechen und analysieren wir regelmäßig das aktuelle Marktgeschehen und zeigen, worauf wir in unserem täglichen Handel achten und stellen gelegentlich eigene Trades vor.

Wir sind davon überzeugt, dass profitabler Börsenhandel erlernbar ist. Es gibt jedoch viel zu viele "Schaufelverkäufer", insb. auch auf den Sozialen Medien, die einem das Blaue vom Himmel versprechen. 
Uns ist es deshalb wichtig, Dir einen realistischen Einblick in unseren täglichen Handel zu geben, und zu zeigen was möglich ist, und was nicht.

snippet.title: TG2000
snippet.description:
Tutti i giorni dal lunedì alla domenica notiziari quotidiani e rubriche di approfondimento. Servizi, interviste, inviati in Italia e nel mondo per raccontare quel che accade e anticipare i grandi eventi, con particolare attenzione alla realtà meno illuminata dai grandi media. Grande attenzione all’affidabilità delle fonti con uno stile non aggressivo; il racconto si affida a uno sguardo diverso, più umano. L’attività del Papa e della Chiesa viene raccontata non per dovere istituzionale ma perché nelle parole e nei gesti di Francesco passa tutti i giorni un contenuto esistenziale che intercetta le domande più importanti di ogni uomo sul senso della vita. Le notizie vengono approfondite con analisi e commenti, per aiutare i telespettatori a discernere e a capire oltre i titoli che scorrono veloci in rete. Cinque edizioni al giorno dal lunedì al sabato: ore 12, 18.30 e 20.45 e due FLASH alle 8.30 e alle 14.55. E due edizioni la domenica ore 18.30 e 20.45.
Direttore: Vincenzo Morgante

snippet.title: University of Birmingham
snippet.description:
The University of Birmingham is one of the most popular UK universities, offering diverse opportunities for study and research.

From 1900 to the present day, the University of Birmingham has been at the forefront of both national and international research, leading the way in making ground-breaking progress in areas that span industries such as gene structure, medicine, space research and communications.
We are changing how the world works. 

A global reputation, quality learning and teaching, excellent facilities, a stunning campus and great city are some of the reasons making Birmingham a great place to study and live.

snippet.title: Österreichische Gesellschaft für Europapolitik
snippet.description:
Die Österreichische Gesellschaft für Europapolitik (ÖGfE) ist ein parteipolitisch unabhängiger Verein
auf sozialpartnerschaftlicher Basis.

Wir informieren über europäische Integration und stehen für einen offenen Dialog über aktuelle europapolitische Fragen und deren Relevanz für Österreich. Wir verfügen über langjährige Erfahrung in Bezug auf die Förderung europäischer Debatten und agieren als Katalysator zur Verbreitung von europapolitischen Informationen und Analysen. Die ÖGfE wurde im Jahr 1991 gegründet und wird finanziert und gebildet von den österreichischen Sozialpartnern und der Oesterreichischen Nationalbank.

snippet.title: Free Thinker
snippet.description:
Think Free Be Free. 

Our channel highlights just some of the bravest human beings on this planet who simply refuse to stand by and watch as their traditions, laws and even thoughts are systematically being destroyed by the very organisations that should be protecting them.
Unrelenting and absolute in their tireless quest for the truth the investigative reporters and writers such as Alex Jones, David Icke, Matt Drudge and Paul Joseph Watson have dedicated their lives to exposing the criminal and sometimes horrifying decisions made by governments and businesses throughout the world.
No matter if you agree or disagree with these titans of independent media you can not deny their unbiased and critical reporting supported by a huge amount of physical and documentary evidence.
Thank you for viewing our channel and be sure to Think Free and you will Be Free!

snippet.title: KOMPASTV
snippet.description:
Perkembangan teknologi informasi secara signifikan berdampak pada kebiasaan konsumsi media masyarakat Indonesia. Menyikapi perubahan tersebut, Kompas Gramedia mengambil langkah-langkah untuk membentengi kehadirannya di ruang media digital melalui KompasTV.

KompasTV berdedikasi untuk menyediakan konten dan pengalaman pengguna dengan kualitas terbaik kepada pemirsanya. Baik melalui televisi berbayar berdefinisi tinggi, streaming gratis, maupun kehadirannya di berbagai platform media sosial, KompasTV dapat diakses dan dinikmati oleh pemirsa setianya.

Selain komitmennya untuk menyajikan konten terbaik, KompasTV dikenal dengan independensi dan kredibilitasnya sebagai stasiun televisi berita. Dengan komitmen yang kuat terhadap kualitas dan pemahaman mendalam tentang lanskap media yang terus berubah, KompasTV berada di posisi yang tepat untuk terus menjadi media terkemuka di tahun-tahun mendatang.

snippet.title: Channels Television
snippet.description:
Channel Television is Africa’s most awarded broadcaster. It is a multiple award-winning 24-hour news and media organization founded in 1995 by Nigerian veteran broadcasters John and Sola Momoh. The Company began operations in Lagos in July 1995 and has since grown to become a global television network with operations all over Nigeria and bureaus in Johannesburg, Dubai, London and Washington DC.  Its international station "Channels24" can be received all over the United Kingdom and parts of Europe.  

The station has bagged the industry’s most coveted award of “Best Television Station Of The Year” a record 16 times (2000-2004, 2008, 2010-2018 and 2020-2022)

Channels Television has over 13.5 million subscribers on Social media and its videos on YouTube have been viewed over 1.4 billion times.

Do not forget to subscribe to this channel for up-to-date news on Nigeria.

snippet.title: m j murcott
snippet.description: Science, fiction and thought provoking ideas. With a little imagination and inventiveness it is possible to improve the world. All provided by your host M J Murcott, some viewers come here for the ASMR, but I am not deliberately creating content for those wanting to experience ASMR. If you like what you find here feel free to share it with your friends, if you think there is a topic I should cover feel free to comment, I am always looking for new subjects. From the 5th Feb 2016  I have been using an upgraded camera, however due to the large number of videos using the older equipment these will still be retained even if the quality isn't as good. Recent changes in lighting have again improved the videos so they look less "ghostly" as one person described it. The channels page now features "the toast train" a podcast I did a couple of interviews on which can be found on the live section of their channel.

snippet.title: CGTN
snippet.description:
China Global Television Network, or CGTN, is an international media organization launched on December 31, 2016. It aims to provide global audiences with accurate and timely news coverage as well as rich audiovisual services, promoting communication and understanding between China and the world, and enhancing cultural exchanges and mutual trust between China and other countries. 

Headquartered in Beijing, CGTN has three production centers, located in Nairobi, Washington D.C. and London, all staffed with international professionals from around the world.

Adhering to the principles of objectivity, rationality and balance in reporting, CGTN endeavors to present information from diverse perspectives.

snippet.title: Duo Look
snippet.description: Blogowe małżeństwo z Wielkiej Brytanii: ONA – Alicja, ON – Jarek. Piszemy jak żyje się w UK, gdzie pojechać na weekend, jak zaplanować wakacje, wybieramy największe atrakcje turystyczne. Każde miejsce poznaje się przez ludzi, jedzenie i zakupy. Dlatego zabieramy was na wyprzedaże, podpowiadamy jak robić tanie zakupy, gdzie znaleźć luksusowe marki oraz jakie pamiątki zabrać z wycieczek. Alicja bardzo lubi przyrodę, kocha książki filmy i o dziwo jest gotowa do testowania nowych technologii. Na szczęście, bo Jarek jest pasjonatem social mediów, Instagrama i technologicznych nowinek. Żartujemy, że na świat patrzymy podwójnie. Po prostu DuoLook. Obecnie mieszkamy w Londynie, ale to dopiero początek podróży ...

snippet.title: Jason Carter
snippet.description:
Jason Carter along with his wife Orsola, street preach across the U.K. and Italy, planting house churches in Italy and the UK, encouraging believers everywhere to meet in homes in accordance with the book of Acts church model.

Prior to this Jason served full time on the pastoral staff of a thriving church in the UK for 14 years, overseeing house groups and the training of house group leaders. 

After experiencing a dramatic wake up call in 2009, Jason turned his attention to warning, writing and teaching on the end of western civilisation. Jason has taught on this subject at Life Bible College and hosted a popular weekly end time prophecy program on Eternal Radio.

Carter is the author of Beyond Earthly Realms, Trumpet Blast Warning and The Great Delusion.

snippet.description:
The European Union continues to expand, extending its reach into an ever greater number of policy areas -- Understanding what makes the EU tick has never been more important. Who wields the real power and influence in Brussels? How will the EU respond to the challenges of economic crisis, climate change and energy security? Will the EU ever develop a meaningful common foreign and security policy?

EU Reporter provides the answers, online and video, with breaking news, incisive analysis and provocative comment on both EU affairs and transatlantic relations.

EU Reporter is widely read by law makers, policy and business decision-makers in Brussels and national capitals around the EU.

snippet.title: euronews (in Italiano)
snippet.description:
Benvenuti al canale Youtube ufficiale di Euronews! 

Tutti i giorni, a tutte le ore, la nostra squadra di 500 giornalisti provenienti da oltre 30 Paesi lavora per raccontarvi l'Europa con assoluta imparzialità. Su questo canale trovate una selezione dei migliori contenuti della TV europea per eccellenza. 

La nostra missione è quella di dare alle persone la possibilità di formarsi una propria opinione. Confidiamo nell'intelligenza e nella capacità delle persone di decidere da sole e cerchiamo di fornire al nostro pubblico la più grande diversità di punti di vista attraverso un giornalismo imparziale.
Ci concentriamo su fatti, idee e soluzioni.
Crediamo che tutti i punti di vista siano importanti.

Euronews è nato dalla volontà di creare un canale d'informazione europeo indipendente. Essendo l'unico media internazionale con una prospettiva europea, Euronews è il luogo a cui si rivolge il mondo per ascoltare ciò che l'Europa ha da dire.

snippet.title: Voice of America
snippet.description:
Voice of America (VOA) is the largest U.S. international broadcaster, providing news and information in more than 40 languages to an estimated weekly audience of 236.8 million people. VOA produces content for digital, television, and radio platforms. It is easily accessed via your mobile phone and on social media. It is also distributed by satellite, cable, FM and MW, and is carried on a network of approximately 3,000 affiliate stations. 

Since its creation in 1942, Voice of America has been committed to providing comprehensive coverage of the news and telling audiences the truth. Through World War II, the Cold War, the fight against global terrorism, and the struggle for freedom around the globe today, VOA exemplifies the principles of a free press.

Актуальные видеоматериалы о последних трендах валютного рынка, ключевых событиях и знаковых фигурах финансового мира будут интересны любому трейдеру вне зависимости от профессионального опыта и торговой стратегии. Вместе с нами вы сможете побывать на международных финансовых выставках, познакомиться с представителями ведущих брокерских компаний, пройтись по улицам мировых финансовых и культурных центров Европы, Азии и Америки.

Каждый день специально для вас сплоченная команда специалистов готовит новые информационные и аналитические выпуски, экспертные интервью и событийные репортажи.

Следите за публикацией свежих видеоматериалов Форекс - телевидения от ГК ИнстаФорекс.

snippet.title: euronews
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official Euronews YouTube channel!

Around the clock, our team of 500 journalists of more than 30 different nationalities gathers news with impartial perspective, beyond the headlines content and voices from across Europe and the world. Our YouTube channel has all this and more, bringing you selected and original content from the world's most trusted news source.

Our mission is to empower people to form their own opinion. We trust in people’s intelligence and ability to make up their own mind and seek to provide our audience with the greatest diversity of viewpoints through journalism that is unapologetically impartial. We don’t trade in bias and outrage, we focus on facts, ideas, and solutions. We believe all views matter.

Euronews was born out of a will to create a strong independent European news channel in 1993. As the only international news media with a European perspective, Euronews is where the world turns to hear what Europe has to say.

Check us out on ⬇️

snippet.title: GreenPartyIreland
snippet.description:
Follow us on twitter at: http://twitter.com/greenparty_ie

The founding principles of the Party are based on peace, democracy, protection of the environment and our natural resources and social justice. We believe in a range of policies to alter things for the better, from properly funded education and a better transport system, to improved primary health care and a fairer tax system. We believe in equality, in a political system that is transparent and in decision-making at community level. We understand that we need to plan now for our future energy needs.
